**Privacy Policy for Nerd Nudge**

Effective Date: 03/11/2024

**Introduction**
Nerd Nudge ("we," "us," or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of information that you may provide through our mobile application.

**Information Collection**
We collect the following types of information:
- Personal Information: Email address, name, and any other information you provide when creating an account.
- Usage Data: Information about how you interact with the app, including features accessed, time spent, and other analytics data.

**Use of Information**
We use the information we collect for the following purposes:
- To provide and maintain our app.
- To improve our app's functionality and user experience.
- To communicate with you regarding updates and promotions.

**Data Sharing**
We do not share your personal information with third parties except:
- To comply with legal obligations.
- To provide services that you have requested.

**User Rights**
You have the right to request access to and deletion of your personal information. Please refer to our account deletion policy for more details.

**Security**
We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access and use.

**Changes to This Policy**
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

**Contact Us**
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at neurosparktech@gmail.com
